<p>I developed a markdown generator software. It's a software where you don't need to remember tags to generate markdowns! Sounds interesting? You just need to simply type as if writing on Microsoft Word, and it will automatically generate a markdown file for you. The interface is very user-friendly. WAIT!!!! I'm not finished yet! If you don't have MS Word on your system, you can also generate a Docx file from here. Also, my software is free! I'm making it open-source. Currently, only Windows users can install this software. If you guys like it and find it useful, I'll build it for Mac and Linux too.</p><p>If you find it helpful, then just buy me coffee.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Here some examples : </strong></p><h1>Markdown syntax guide</h1><h2><br></h2><h2>Headers</h2><h1><br></h1><h1>This is a Heading h1</h1><h2><br></h2><h2>This is a Heading h2</h2><h2><br></h2><h2>Emphasis</h2><p><em>This text will be italic</em></p><p><em>This will also be italic</em></p><p><strong>This text will be bold</strong></p><p><strong>This will also be bold</strong></p><p><em>You&nbsp;can&nbsp;combine them</em></p><h2><br></h2><h2>Lists</h2><h3><br></h3><h3>Unordered</h3><ul><li>Item 1</li><li>Item 2</li><li>Item 2a</li><li>Item 2b</li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3>Ordered</h3><ol><li>Item 1</li><li>Item 2</li><li>Item 3</li><li>Item 3a</li><li>Item 3b</li></ol><h2><br></h2><h2>Images</h2><p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p><p><br></p><h2>Videos</h2><p><br></p><iframe class="ql-video" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/o-XHNZXqOGM?showinfo=0"></iframe><p><br></p><h2>Links</h2><p>My Spotify <a href="https://open.spotify.com/album/76WxXnJyFnkeaAPI3hj2yY" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">link</a></p><p>Facebook <a href="https://www.facebook.com/esh.romanch/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">link</a></p>
